 # Add a google mail as the outgoing mail server;
 # Create a project and an issue;
 # Attach an image to the issue;
 # Add a comment to the issue:
{noformat:bgColor=#f8f8f8}
!my-attachment.png!
{noformat}

h3. Expected Behavior

The email notification would show the attached image.
h3. Actual Results

The notification does not display the image attached.
 !Screen Shot 2015-01-16 at 7.43.36 PM.png!
h3. Notes

The problem with Avatars not being shown in the email notifications is now being tracked here:
